==English==
===Etymology===
From the [[w:Ojibwe language|Ojibwe]] word ''[[ajidamoo]]'', "red squirrel."

===Noun===
'''chipmunk''' (''plural'' '''chipmunks''')

#A [[squirrel]]-like [[rodent]] of the genus ''[[Tamias]]'', native mainly to North America.

====Synonyms====
*[[ground squirrel]], [[striped squirrel]]

